WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.800
Hello and welcome to Let's Learn English with Anna.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:16.200
I am Dr. Jill. but who are you?

00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:19.080
Today we answer that question.

00:00:19.080 --> 00:00:22.320
Who are you?

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:25.080
So let's go to Anna's treehouse.

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:27.960
She helps us answer the question.

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:30.960
Who are you?

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:35.440
Hi. welcome to my treehouse.

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.400
I am Anna.

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:39.720
And I am Max.

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:40.720
That is Max.

00:00:40.720 --> 00:00:43.720
Max is a mailbox.

00:00:43.720 --> 00:00:47.440
Anna. I have our question for today.

00:00:47.440 --> 00:00:50.520
Thanks Max.

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:52.880
Who are you?

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:54.880
Who are you?

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:57.680
I am Anna.

00:00:57.680 --> 00:00:59.680
I am Anna.

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:01.680
I am Max.

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:03.680
I am Max.

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:05.680
Max. I'm not done yet.

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:07.680
Oh sorry.

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:17.680
Max. I'm done now.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:21.680
And I am Max.

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:25.480
Nice song.

00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:30.480
Okay friends. say the question after me.

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:33.480
Who are you?

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:37.480
Who are you?

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:41.480
Now. let's meet some new friends.

00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:45.480
They answer today's question too.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:48.480
I am Zenitsu.

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:50.480
I am Ana Avery.

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:52.480
Hi. I am Alexa.

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:56.480
How many friends do you see?

00:01:56.480 --> 00:02:01.480
One. two. three.

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:04.480
That's right. three friends.

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:09.480
Okay. now let's play a game with our friends.

00:02:09.480 --> 00:02:11.480
They say their names.

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:13.480
You listen.

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:15.480
Are you ready?

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:17.480
Here they are.

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:20.480
Find the names with the letter A.

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:24.480
I am Zenitsu.

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:28.480
I am Ana Avery.

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:32.480
Hi. I am Alexa.

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:37.480
That's right.

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:41.480
Alexa and Anna have the letter A.

00:02:41.480 --> 00:02:43.480
Good job.

00:02:43.480 --> 00:02:46.480
Now. let's go back to Anna's treehouse.

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:50.480
She talks about other words with the letter A.

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:51.480
Let's go.

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:53.480
Who are you?

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:55.480
Who are you?

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:57.480
I am Anna.

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:01.480
Anna starts with an A.

00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:06.480
But the letter A has many sounds.

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:09.480
A. Ape.

00:03:09.480 --> 00:03:12.480
A. Apple.

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:15.480
A. Anna.

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:19.480
Anna ate an apple.

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:24.480
Who are you?

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:26.480
Who are you?

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:28.480
I am Max.

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:31.480
You are Anna.

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:34.480
Who are you?

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:37.480
Who am I?

00:03:39.480 --> 00:03:42.480
I need to walk.

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:46.480
Who am I?

00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:48.480
Who?

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:50.480
Who?

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.480
Who are you?

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:57.480
You are an owl.

00:03:57.480 --> 00:03:59.480
One owl.

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:01.480
Two owls.

00:04:01.480 --> 00:04:04.480
Three owls.

00:04:04.480 --> 00:04:06.480
I love owls.

00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:08.480
Three owls.

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:11.480
I love owls.

00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:13.480
And I love to walk.

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:15.480
Anna. it's time to go.

00:04:15.480 --> 00:04:16.480
Thanks. Max.

00:04:16.480 --> 00:04:18.480
Come back again. though.

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:19.480
Goodbye.

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:21.480
Now. you try it.

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:23.480
Ask your family and friends.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:26.480
Who are you?

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:29.480
How do they answer?

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:31.480
I am Zenitsu.

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:33.480
I am Ana Avery.

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:35.480
Hi. I am Alexa.

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:39.480
See you next time on Let's Learn English with Anna.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:42.480
Anna. I am Anna.

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:45.480
I am Anna.

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:47.480
I am Anna.

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:49.480
I am Anna.

